testCodes.label: Lyme Exposure
testCodes.description: Lyme exposure is actually exposure to the bacteria borrelia.  This bacteria is not contagious, and cannot be spread to humans or other animals. We may need more testing to determine if Dido has an active disease.

testCodes.label: Ehrlichia Exposure
testCodes.description: We may need more testing to determine if Dido has an active disease. Dido is not contagious and cannot spread this infection to any dogs or people.
